subject: Tinder - change of terms
text:
Hi.

Tinder (https://www.gotinder.com/privacy) has not been rated for the addon yet.

I'd like it noted that they only notify users of changes to the privacy policy if they are 'material
changes'. 'Material changes' is not defined.
All changes are instant. Consent to the changes is assumed.

> If we make any material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you of the changes by
reasonable means, which could include notifications through the Services or via email. Please review
the changes carefully. Your continued use of the Services following the posting of changes to this
policy will mean you consent to and accept those changes. 


Regards
Matt
